<p class="indent2" style="-uslm-lc:I13" xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">The base period taken into account for purposes of paragraph (1)(B) with respect to individuals separating from service with the employer before <date date="1995-01-01">January 1, 1995</date>, is the calendar quarter beginning October 1 of the calendar year preceding the calendar year in which such separation occurs.</p>
